 [https://leetcode.com/problems/trapping-rain-water/solutions/3387829/cjavapythonjavascript-brute-force-optimized-code-easy-to-understand-for-begineers/](https://leetcode.com/problems/trapping-rain-water/solutions/3387829/cjavapythonjavascript-brute-force-optimized-code-easy-to-understand-for-begineers/)
