2. less than height[0]     (new height will be less than height[0] i.e less than previous height (0,8))
3. equal to height[0]    (same as of earlier)

so width is decreasing and height is also decreasing/constant . no need to check for (0,1)...(0,7) discard them and increase pointer from 0 to 1.(increase the pointer from  where the height is less).

