# Intuition
Two pointer approach to solve this problem

# Approach
1. use two pointers , keep ***s at start*** and ***e at end***.
2. move the pointer with lower height only
3. we have to calculate the area and keep the maximum in the ***maxArea*** variable everytime
4. return maxArea

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
O(n)

- Space complexity:
O(1)

# Code
