1.point the two pointer left and right on the height
2. claculate the maximum area of container .
3. width = right - left 
4. heigth_of_container = min(height[left],height[right])
5. take min heigth to avoid overflow of water
6. now calculate area = width * heigth_of_container
7. the after that check condition if height[left] < height[right] just increment the left pointer left++;
8. just like that if height[right] < height[left] decrement the right pointer right--
9. bor base case if both the left and rigth hiegth became equal just increment left++ ande decrement right-- 

